OL,5, Embattled Chinese property giant       
OL,6, Evergrande has announced plans for     
OL,7, restructuring around $20bn (#16.2bn) in
OL,8, offshore debt, which could be seen as a
OL,9, model for other struggling developers. 
OL,11,FThe firm said the measures will help   
OL,12,F"efforts to resume operations and      
OL,13,Fresolve issues on shore".              
OL,15,FEvergrande has more than $300bn in     
OL,16,Fliabilities and defaulted on its debts 
OL,17,Fin late 2021.                          
OL,19,FThe crisis has spooked traders who fear
OL,20,Fcontagion in China's property sector.  
